{"tid":309461,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"A7R2 經 ipad 過相一問, 真心求敎","createTime":"2017-07-05T04:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T08:44:19.000Z","uid":33267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24eac1d9d613f54346fb26de99e4d5c588103b74","tid":309461,"uid":33267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"最近入手A7R2, 存 RAW + JPEG, 亂影一日有成30G以上.<br />\n黎緊外遊14日, 老老實實, 最少500G野, 真心唔想帶NOTEBOOK + EXTERNAL HARDISK.<br />\n<br />\n之前追POST, 如果經IPAD lighting - SDcard dongle, 由LIGHTROOM過相, 再upload上google drive, 30G一晚都未必過得完. 再講, 歐洲酒店WIFI會令呢件事變成mission impossible.<br />\n<br />\n真係諗到頭都爆.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲有計? <br />\n有又無巴絲試過 ipad + portable hardisk 呢個方案?<br />\n<br />\n真心求敎, 要插唔緊要, 不過細力些少.<br />\nthanks in advance."},{"pid":"a70624a5bba4c2c4ad6858ffe04d6919c2479233","tid":309461,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:04:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a97f9e98f2892bf0ac556b46ebf6980d814373ec","tid":309461,"uid":113073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:16:30.000Z","msg":"影咁多raw都汁唔哂啦<br />\n<br />\n高反差先用raw.平時jpg執得唔過份都夠用掛<br />\n<br />\n一係買多兩張128gb.<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就唔好用盡42mp.調低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9a7f161f51efaac97ac3aed676499f1e6807f7","tid":309461,"uid":33267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"用ipad睇相，效果比相機mon仔睇，快靚正，好太多，朝早影，食晏睇。<br />\n<br />\n部ipad得256G, 又食唔晒500G相。<br />\n有無巴絲有類似煩惱？"},{"pid":"2db6e0659a7158a2c2f95a02e4f5bf95295aab1e","tid":309461,"uid":33267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影咁多raw都汁唔哂啦<br />\n<br />\n高反差先用raw.平時jpg執得唔過份都夠用掛<br />\n<br />\n一係買多兩張128gb.<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就唔好用盡42mp.調低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄講得啱，執就執唔晒㗎啦，不過唔留raw好似唔係咁好，畢竟有D景點去過一次唔會再去。<br />\n<br />\n買卡都有諗過，但買多3張128G成$1400，只用一次好嘥，平日香港影根本用唔到咁多張卡。"},{"pid":"2ad42eb9997ec834cf1eddbae1052ee27274a433","tid":309461,"uid":123819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:45:41.000Z","msg":"帶notebook 同 hdd 咪解決左囉<br />\n根本都唔係問題黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1435d3f6309fdd39ac74e1fea928ffadcaf7d65d","tid":309461,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:02:12.000Z","msg":"A7R2 好唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f690e0aa9f6b96999a2c5cfa5ff2043e3ded96","tid":309461,"uid":3005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:05:49.000Z","msg":"買隻呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sandisk.hk/home/mobile-device-storage/ixpand\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandisk.hk%2Fhome%2Fmobile-device-storage%2Fixpand&d=%2F%2FQmoH%2FgMcs2fxRgan34Xr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=263e8994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sandisk.hk/home/mobile-device-storage/ixpand</a>"},{"pid":"fa35fc61d26557e371681568a60ae078e7df0748","tid":309461,"uid":92906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:00:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買隻呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sandisk.hk/home/mobile-device-storage/ixpand\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandisk.hk%2Fhome%2Fmobile-device-storage%2Fixpand&d=%2F%2FQmoH%2FgMcs2fxRgan34Xr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=263e8994\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sandisk.hk/home/mobile-device-storage/ixpand</a></blockquote><br />\n睇落好胖點知一睇貴到呢<br />\n32g 488<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\